    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Ah, ok. Yeah, the behavior is expected; if the environment variable is loaded in `setUp` but you try to reference it outside of functions it will not work, since variable declarations etc. are processed during contract creation (which is before `setUp` is called). Will close this in favor of #2131 since the task in that issue is to be more aware of when we panic and when we bubble errors up :)",
